        <title>The author</title>
    </properties>
    <body>
        <p>Andreas Veithen was born in 1977 in <a href="http://www.st.vith.be/index_english.htm">Sankt Vith</a> (<a href="http://www.eastbelgium.com/">eastern part of Belgium</a>).</p>
        <p>After getting his BSc and MSc in theoretical physics, he was a research fellow at the <a href="http://www.ucl.be/en/">Catholic University of Louvain</a>.</p>
        <p>In 2002 he started to work for <a href="http://www.it-optics.com/">it-optics</a>, a small company focusing on Open Source services.</p>
        <p>Since 2005 he is a developer at <a href="http://www.gfi.be/">GFI Benelux</a>, where he mainly works on Java projects.</p>
